text: Alqomar Tehupelasury (born 16 June 1995) is an Indonesian footballer who currently plays as a Midfielder for PSPS Pekanbaru.Alqomar Tehupelasury ==Career== ===PSPS Pekanbaru=== In 2017, Alqomar joined PSPS Pekanbaru in the 2017 Liga 2.PSPS kembali datangkan eks-timnas U-19 ==International career== He made his international debut for Indonesia U-19 on 10 September 2013, and scoring one goal against Brunei U-19.Piala AFF U-19: Indonesia 5-0 Brunei Darussalam ===International goals=== International under-19 goals {| class="wikitable" |- !
